    dc:description "Figs 34–38. Cracticotaenia adelaidae sp. nov. 34. Scolex. 35. Detail of hooks crowns. 36. Hooks: anterior (A) and posterior (B). 37. Mature proglottis. 38. Eggs. Scale bars: 34 = 100 µm; 35 = 10 µm; 19 = 500 µm; 36, 38 = 20 µm; 37 = 250 µm." ;
